channel.title: My teleports
channel.description:
please someone help me fix my teleports, i cant get them to work and its really stressing me out!! ive changed the description on each teleport to "Monster", "Skills", etc but i cannot for the life of me get them to teleport me to the correct places... this is a PI source btw.
heres my pastebin http://pastebin.com/cyzqPBw5

item.title: My teleports
item.dc:creator: @Vazzily Vazzily
item.description:
@Vazzily wrote:

If you have a Z-FileSearcher, go to one of these

case 6004: //ardy c.getDH().sendOption5("Mining", "Smithing", "Woodcutting&Fletching","Fishing&Cooking", "Farming"); c.teleAction = 1111;//any number.. Remember this number ^__^ break;

and either search for the 1111 from the teleAction and search for it in your source with the z file searcher, or search for [code]6004 with it which is your case id
then you might find the coords located somewhere else

if you dont have the file searcher rip it off another source
